'''唐納德·萊昂·布朗肯西普'''（{{lang-en|Donald Leon Blankenship}}；{{bd|1950年|3月14日}}），是一位美國業務主管和曾被判罪的犯人，也曾是美國第六大[[煤|煤]]業公司<ref name="EIA">{{cite web|url=http://www.eia.doe.gov/cneaf/coal/page/acr/table10.html|title=Major U.S. Coal Producers|date=2009-09-18|publisher=[[Energy_Information_Administration|Energy Information Administration]]|accessdate=2010-04-07|archive-date=2011-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430180441/http://www.eia.doe.gov/cneaf/coal/page/acr/table10.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>——{{le|梅西能源|Massey Energy}}自2000年到2010年的行政總裁<ref>T Allen, "[http://blog.riskmetrics.com/gov/2010/12/investors-tour-role-in-massey-leadership-change.html Investors Tout Their Role in Massey's Leadership Change] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.riskmetrics.com/gov/2010/12/investors-tour-role-in-massey-leadership-change.html |date=20110208020759 }}" (December 7, 2010) Riskmetrics</ref>。

2015年12月3日，布朗肯西普被裁定在{{le|上大分支礦難|Upper Big Branch Mine disaster}}中犯下違反礦山安全和健康標準的罪名，被判入獄一年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wchstv.com/news/features/eyewitness-news/stories/Jurors-Convict-Don-Blankenship-On-Conspiracy-Charge-238644.shtml |title=Jurors Convict Don Blankenship On Conspiracy Charge - WCHS - ABC |accessdate=2017-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205090625/http://www.wchstv.com/news/features/eyewitness-news/stories/Jurors-Convict-Don-Blankenship-On-Conspiracy-Charge-238644.shtml |archivedate=2015-12-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他經常就政治、環境、工會和煤炭議題生產發聲，曾在{{le|2018年西弗吉尼亞州美國參議院議員選舉|2018 United States Senate election in West Virginia|2018年}}[[西弗吉尼亞州|西弗吉尼亞州]][[美國參議院|美國參議院]]選舉共和黨初選名列第三，敗給{{le|帕特里克·莫里西|Patrick Morrisey}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollcall.com/news/politics/patrick-morrisey-wins-west-virginia-gop-senate-primary|title=Patrick Morrisey Wins West Virginia GOP Senate Primary|work=Roll Call|first=Simone|last=Pathé|date=2018-05-08|accessdate=2020-09-02|archive-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022125005/https://www.rollcall.com/news/politics/patrick-morrisey-wins-west-virginia-gop-senate-primary|dead-url=no}}</ref>，隨後他以引用虛假信息、政治骯髒以及個人不願退出為由<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.donblankenship.com/view_post.php?id=80|title=Don Blankenship: American Competitionist|website=www.donblankenship.com|language=en|access-date=2018-08-16|archive-date=2018-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918104014/http://www.donblankenship.com/view_post.php?id=80|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，試圖用[[憲法黨_(美國)|憲法黨]]候選人身份參選，卻未能列入選票，不久他轉而支持莫里西<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/2018/05/21/politics/west-virginia-don-blankenship-third-party-senate-run/index.html|title=Still fighting McConnell, Don Blankenship launches third-party Senate bid in West Virginia|work=CNN|access-date=2018-08-16|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109015307/https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/2018/05/21/politics/west-virginia-don-blankenship-third-party-senate-run/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>thehill.com May 21, 2018: [http://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/388706-blankenship-third-party-bid-worries-senate-gop ''Blankenship third-party bid worries Senate GOP''] {{Wayback|url=http://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/388706-blankenship-third-party-bid-worries-senate-gop |date=20201210000930 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Blankenship to wage third-party bid after losing primary|url=https://www.politico.com/story/2018/05/21/don-blankenship-third-party-constitution-party-600779|website=POLITICO|accessdate=2020-09-02|archive-date=2019-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725181045/https://www.politico.com/story/2018/05/21/don-blankenship-third-party-constitution-party-600779|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

布朗肯西普在2019年10月18日或19日於憲法黨全國代表大會中宣布代表憲法黨[[2020年美國總統選舉|競逐總統職務]]<ref name=launchcampaign1>{{cite web|url=https://ballot-access.org/2019/10/20/don-blankenship-speaks-at-constitution-party-national-committee-meeting/|title=Don Blankenship declares for Constitution Party presidential nomination|website=Ballot Access News|date=2019-10-20|last1=Winger|first1=Richard|accessdate=2019-12-25|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125024605/http://ballot-access.org/2019/10/20/don-blankenship-speaks-at-constitution-party-national-committee-meeting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，根據憲法黨網站，他的競選搭檔為{{le|威廉·摩爾|William Mohr|比爾·摩爾}}。

